overview: Developed a set of illustrations for Simmerthingz, a gaming content creator, including emotes, Twitch alerts, and a motion graphic for a YouTube outro.  his included emotes, twitch alerts, and a youtube outro motion graphic.
process:
Tools: Procreate, DaVinci Studio, Adobe AfterEffects
Client provided reference images and we worked together to create pieces that matched their vision
challenges: This was my first project working with motion graphics, I was very grateful to Simmerthingz and their patience with me as I learned new software as I worked on this project.
